{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Smooth"], "type": "title", "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "text": ["Smooths out (or \"relaxes\") polygons, meshes and curves without increasing the number of points."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "text": ["This node rearranges the existing points in the geometry to reduce roughness."]}, {"body": [{"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "text": ["To smooth by increasing the number of points, use the ", {"_hs_sc": true, "text": ["Subdivide node"], "value": "/nodes/sop/subdivide", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/subdivide", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link"}, "."]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "text": ["To smooth by brushing over the object, use the ", {"_hs_sc": true, "text": ["Sculpt tool"], "value": "/nodes/sop/sculpt", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/sculpt", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link"}, " and set one of the mouse buttons to \"Smooth\"."]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "text": ["Smooth can also smooth any floating-point attributes, including color and texture coordinates."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "text": ["Select the points, facets, or object you want to smooth."]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "text": ["Click the ", {"_hs_sc": true, "text": "", "value": "SOP/smooth", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/SOP/smooth", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link"}, {"_hs_sc": true, "text": ["Smooth"], "value": "/nodes/sop/smooth", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/smooth", "scheme": null, "type": "link"}, " tool on the ", {"text": ["Polygon"], "type": "ui"}, " tab."]}], "container": true, "type": "ord_group"}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "text": ["You can change the smoothing specifications in the ", {"_hs_sc": true, "text": ["parameter editor"], "value": "/ref/panes/parms", "fullpath": "/ref/panes/parms", "scheme": null, "type": "link"}, "."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "text": ["If you only want to smooth certain areas of your object, use the ", {"_hs_sc": true, "text": "", "value": "SOP/sculpt", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/SOP/sculpt", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link"}, {"_hs_sc": true, "text": ["sculpt"], "value": "sculpt", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/sculpt", "scheme": null, "type": "link"}, " tool."]}], "indent": 0, "role": "item", "type": "note"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "note_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Using Smooth"], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "text": ["Subset of primitives to smooth."]}], "indent": 0, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Group"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "text": ["Lets you specify that the boundaries of the selection (the ", {"text": ["Group"], "type": "ui"}, " field) or the surface should not move."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "text": ["No points are locked in place. Any point in the selection may move."]}], "indent": 4, "type": "dt", "text": ["None"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "text": ["Boundary edges are locked in place. Smoothing will not affect them."]}], "indent": 4, "type": "dt", "text": ["Unshared Edges"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "text": ["Boundary edges ", {"text": ["and"], "type": "strong"}, " the outside edges of the selection are locked in place. Smoothing will not affect them."]}], "indent": 4, "type": "dt", "text": ["Group Boundary"]}], "container": true, "type": "dt_group"}], "indent": 0, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Constrained Boundary"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "text": ["A list of points to lock in place, so smoothing will not affect them. You can click the ", {"_hs_sc": true, "text": "", "value": "BUTTONS/reselect", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/BUTTONS/reselect", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link"}, " Select button to the right of the field and select the vertices interactively in the viewport."]}], "indent": 0, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Constrained Points"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "text": ["The attributes to smooth. Multiple attributes can be smoothed at the same time. The drop-down menu to the right of the field has the most common attributes to smooth, ", {"text": ["P"], "type": "code"}, " (point position) and ", {"text": ["uv"], "type": "code"}, " (texture coordinates). If the field is blank, the node smooths ", {"text": ["all"], "type": "em"}, " position-type attributes."]}], "indent": 0, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Attributes"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "text": ["Lets you choose different smoothing models that have different effects on the point positions. "]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "text": ["Move points so they're evenly spaced."]}], "indent": 4, "type": "dt", "text": ["Uniform"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "text": ["Move points trying to mainting their original relative distances from one another."]}], "indent": 4, "type": "dt", "text": ["Scale-Dominant"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "text": ["Move points to smooth the curvature while trying to maintain their original arrangement."]}], "indent": 4, "type": "dt", "text": ["Curvature-Dominant"]}], "container": true, "type": "dt_group"}], "indent": 0, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Method"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "text": ["How much to smooth the selected points. Higher values move the points farther from their original positions."]}], "indent": 0, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Strength"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "text": ["Higher values preserve finer details from the original mesh. Lower values are faster and smooth more."]}, {"indent": 4, "type": "para", "text": ["A lower number of passes is more efficient for producing significant smoothing on larger meshes."]}], "indent": 0, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Filter Quality"]}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Parameters", "role": "section", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "id": "parameters"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "text": [{"_hs_sc": true, "text": "", "value": "/nodes/sop/deltamush", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/deltamush", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "text": [{"_hs_sc": true, "text": "", "value": "/nodes/sop/divide", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/divide", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "text": [{"_hs_sc": true, "text": "", "value": "/nodes/sop/fit", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/fit", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "text": [{"_hs_sc": true, "text": "", "value": "/nodes/sop/sculpt", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/sculpt", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "text": [{"_hs_sc": true, "text": "", "value": "/nodes/sop/subdivide", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/subdivide", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link"}]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Related", "role": "section", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "id": "related"}], "summary": ["Smooths out (or \"relaxes\") polygons, meshes and curves without increasing the number of points."], "type": "root", "attrs": {"version": "2.0", "tags": "reshape, model, cleanup, core, smooth", "namespace": null, "internal": "smooth::2.0", "context": "sop", "type": "node", "icon": "SOP/smooth"}, "title": ["Smooth"]}